{
  "stem": "19210.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 469.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were several Hungary and Romanian Jews that stayed in Nahariya, became friends later on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one of them was, was a boxing, my boxing partner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lotzi ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Farkash. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he became a general contractor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And basically, that-- our assistance to that was to help him at times with the language.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But primarily, the, the Jewish Sochnut, the Jewish Agency, provided a tremendous amount of help by means of teaching him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Teaching them Hebrew so they could communicate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because communication was always a barrier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, with so many languages, it would be difficult.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, so the Jewish Agency had, you might call it not a school, but I can't remember exactly the name-- ulpan.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had many, many ulpans everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So within a few days, a few weeks, you could speak Hebrew, at least the necessary Hebrew that-- to communicate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So basically, that's where we are with the immigrants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were, there were such times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the Haganah agents in-- there were, obviously, agents throughout Europe and other countries.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to make the arrangements to bring in all kinds of arms and ammunitions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In, in one instance that I know of was by bringing arms hidden into these highway roller trucks, you know, that after they put the asphalt down and you pave with this huge rollers?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, they used to fill these huge rollers with arms and ammunitions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was before the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the war, as the war started, of course, the largest shipment of arms came from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and thanks to that, thanks to God to that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because without that, we were-- we did not have any, much arms at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
